Django (Backend)

Python web framework
Server side framework
Designed to get you start fast

Web framework:
    is a collection of modules, packages and libraries Designed to speed up developement

Building API's with Dj is easy:
    Dj + Dj Rest framework

MVT Designe Pattern:
    Modal: Data Access Layer
    View: Business Logic
    Template: Presebtation Layer
